@startuml jes_autopatzer

actor User
participant "React UI" as UI
participant "Electron App" as Electron
participant "Perl Script" as Perl
participant "Teensy (Arduino)" as Teensy
participant "Stepper Motors" as Motors
participant "Hall Effect Sensors" as Sensors
participant "Electromagnet" as Magnet
participant "Lichess API" as Lichess

User -> UI : Interact
UI <-> Electron : User actions/updates
Electron <-> Lichess : WebSocket connection
Electron <-> Perl : Send/receive commands
Perl <-> Teensy : Serial communication
Teensy -> Motors : Control movement
Teensy -> Magnet : Activate/deactivate
Teensy <- Sensors : Read piece positions
Teensy -> Perl : Send board state
Perl -> Electron : Update board state
Electron -> UI : Update display
UI -> User : Show game state

@enduml